Source: pgmqtt
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cargo, clang
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/RayElg/pgmqtt

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgmqtt
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pgmqtt
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Embedded MQTT broker powered by PostgreSQL CDC
 pgmqtt embeds an MQTT broker inside PostgreSQL and publishes change data
 capture events through a pgrx extension. This package builds the extension
 for PostgreSQL 14 through 18 with cargo-pgrx 0.17.0.
